metadata.name: EasterEgg #1
metadata.description: EasterEggz is more than just a Nft - it's a part of play-to-earn game inspired by WolfGames. Stake your Nfts to earn exclusive Tokens or a share of the project's revenue, play interactive games to earn more tokens, vote on future designs and charitable causes, trade your NFTs on our marketplace, and even bid on rare and exclusive EasterEggz in our exciting auctions.
